                            <comment id="473348" author="JIRAUSER19233" created="Tue, 30 Sep 2025 04:04:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well this is similar to an issue that we faced while writing the patch, it seems like the 4K writes are getting grouped together into the 64K bucket, at least initially... except it would need 160 4K writes to make up the additional 10 writes that appear in the 64K bucket so I&apos;m not too sure how that&apos;s happening. I don&apos;t think the entire patch needs to be reverted, the test can just be skipped when this issue occurs, at least until the underlying issue is resolved.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
